Class World

  • java.lang.Object
    • MichaelPriest.World

  • public class World
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds collections of critical data that the simulation needs to function, including a list of herbivores, carnivores, food and rocks.
    Author:
    Michael Priest
    See Also:
    Carnivore, Herbivore, AFood, ARock
